        <title>Quick Change</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;Wow!  Im am thuroughly impressed with Jekyll and how easy it is to put together.  It&#39;s incredible!  I come from a Wordpress background.  I&#39;ve been toying around with Wordpress for the last 6 or seven years and, like most people, was my go to CMS for putting together a website.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Over the years, however, as the system expanded it became very clunky.  It can do a lot and is extremely extendable but that comes at a cost, lots of code.  A lots of code.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Meet &lt;a href=&quot;http://jekyllrb.com/&quot;&gt;Jekyll&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
